FormValidator-Simple-Plugin-Number-Phone-US version 0.0.1

This module adds United States phone number validation to
FormValidator::Simple


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

Alternatively, to install with Module::Build, you can use the following commands:

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install


DEPENDENCIES

FormValidator::Simple
Number::Phone:US


